data.description: You will love this 5 bedroom home with amazing location to Hwy 34, shopping, schools and parks! This home features vaulted ceilings, luxury vinyl plank floors, spacious living room upstairs and a new dishwasher credit! Raised deck for convenient entertaining or BBQs.  3 beds on main with en suite primary access. Lower level offers large garden level family room with ample sunshine, 2 additional beds and laundry. Solar panels are owned and will be paid off at closing!
